{
  "hook": "Stop! Before you hit 'Order PCB'...",
  "headline": "PCB Design Review Checklist Before Fab",
  "body": [
    "Catch costly errors before they become expensive respins",
    "Every missed check = wasted time and money",
    "Run this checklist. Every. Single. Time."
  ],
  "insight": "A thorough design review checklist can eliminate up to 80% of PCB respins. The most common mistakes are trace width errors, missing decoupling caps, and skipping DRC.",
  "source": "Altium, Cadence PCB Design Resources",
  "source_url": "https://resources.altium.com/p/pcb-design-and-review-checklist",
  "pillar": "education",
  "account": "cu-circuits",
  "hashtags": ["#PCBDesign", "#PCBChecklist", "#DesignForManufacturing", "#DFM", "#ElectronicsDesign", "#CuCircuits", "#HardwareEngineering", "#MakeInIndia"],
  "caption": "Stop. Before you send that Gerber file, run through this checklist.\n\nWe see it every week at Cu Circuits: boards that come back with avoidable errors. Wrong trace widths. Missing decoupling caps. Silkscreen over pads. Drill holes too close to the edge.\n\nThese are not complex problems. They are checklist problems.\n\nHere are 10 critical checks every hardware engineer should run before hitting 'Order PCB.' Save this post. Print it. Tape it to your monitor.\n\nBecause a $5 checklist review today saves a $500 respin next week.\n\nWhich check do you most often forget? Drop it in the comments.\n\n#PCBDesign #PCBChecklist #DesignForManufacturing #DFM #ElectronicsDesign #CuCircuits #HardwareEngineering #MakeInIndia",
  "strategy": {"format": "checklist_scorecard", "visual_approach": "green checkmarks and priority badges with category grouping"},
  "html": "<div style=\"width:1080px; height:1350px; background:#0a0a0a; position:relative; overflow:hidden; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;\">\n\n  <!-- Subtle grid bg -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:100%; background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,102,68,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,102,68,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 54px 54px;\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Top accent line -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:0; left:0; width:100%; height:3px; background:#006644;\"></div>\n\n  <!-- Cu Logo: 36x36 green square -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:40px; left:48px; width:36px; height:36px; background:#006644; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; letter-spacing:0.5px;\">Cu</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Label -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:44px; left:100px;\">\n    <span style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Design Review</span>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Hero stat -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:100px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:180px; font-weight:900; color:#006644; line-height:0.9; letter-spacing:-8px;\">80%+</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:24px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top:12px; letter-spacing:1px;\">of PCB errors caught with this checklist</div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Divider -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:340px; left:48px; width:80px; height:2px; background:#006644;\"></div>\n\n  <!-- ELECTRICAL category -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:366px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:14px;\">Electrical</div>\n\n    <!-- Item 1 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Run DRC with zero errors</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">No warnings, no exceptions before export</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 2 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Verify trace widths for current</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Use a calculator for all power lines</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 3 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Decoupling caps on every IC</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">100nF close to VCC pins, short traces</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#cc3333; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">CRITICAL</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 4 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">LVS check: layout matches schematic</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Board netlist must equal schematic exactly</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- MECHANICAL category -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:700px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:14px;\">Mechanical</div>\n\n    <!-- Item 5 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Board outline and mounting holes</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Mechanical fit with enclosure confirmed</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 6 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Drill sizes and annular rings</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Minimum annular ring per your fab spec</div></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 7 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Test points for debug access</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Probe points on key signals and power rails</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- MANUFACTURING category -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; top:968px; left:48px; right:48px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35); letter-spacing:4px; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:14px;\">Manufacturing</div>\n\n    <!-- Item 8 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Silkscreen clear of pads</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">No silkscreen overlapping solderable areas</div></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#b86e00; color:#fff; font-size:11px; font-weight:700; padding:3px 10px; border-radius:3px; letter-spacing:1px;\">HIGH</div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 9 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Copper pour connected, no islands</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Ground plane fully stitched, no floating copper</div></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Item 10 -->\n    <div style=\"display:flex; align-items:center; padding:14px 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"22\" height=\"22\" viewBox=\"0 0 22 22\" style=\"flex-shrink:0; margin-right:16px;\"><rect width=\"22\" height=\"22\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#006644\"/><path d=\"M6 11l3.5 3.5L16 8\" stroke=\"#fff\" stroke-width=\"2.5\" fill=\"none\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg>\n      <div style=\"flex:1;\"><div style=\"font-size:19px; font-weight:700; color:#fff;\">Inspect Gerbers in a viewer</div><div style=\"font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); margin-top:2px;\">Visual check of every layer before sending to fab</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Bottom stat bar -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:80px; left:48px; right:48px; display:flex; gap:16px;\">\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(204,51,51,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Avg Respin Cost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#cc3333; margin-top:4px;\">$2,500</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(184,110,0,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Time Lost</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#b86e00; margin-top:4px;\">2 Weeks</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"flex:1; border:1px solid rgba(0,102,68,0.25); padding:16px; text-align:center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:16px; font-weight:300; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;\">Errors Caught</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:36px; font-weight:900; color:#006644; margin-top:4px;\">80%+</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Footer -->\n  <div style=\"position:absolute; bottom:28px; left:48px; right:48px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.25);\">cucircuits.com</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:12px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Source: Altium, Cadence PCB Design Resources</div>\n  </div>\n\n</div>"
}
